  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: We could show USD (or other currency) value of transaction and transaction cost in Transaction Details screen: \r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/42748987-6e309b7a-88e2-11e8-80b2-77fd6ba3109b.png\" width=\"200\">\r\n\r\nWhich is how how a transaction is shown on Etherscan: \r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/42749061-c386718a-88e2-11e8-9fb2-d9ae4c6104ab.png\" width=\"400\">\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTransaction Details shows fiat value of transaction and transaction fee in selected currency.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nTransaction Details does not show fiat value.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Send or receive a transaction\r\n- Open Transaction Details from Wallet\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.22\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
